Title: Fix refresh of pending changes on bulk service discovery
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1683874631
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.3.0b1

If you used "Run bulk service discovery" in "Setup" - "Hosts" and started the
discovery, the pending changes were not updated after the background job was
finished. A manual reload of the page was needed.


